Michelle Pettigrove https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michelle_Pettigrove 0 Michelle Pettigrove is an Australian actress, well known for her role as Kate Bryant in the long-running rural soap opera A Country Practice.Pettigrove has also appeared in several other series, including Blue Heelers, Home and Away, Something in the Air, Silversun and the mini-series Brides of Christ.
